txt.en: Frogildi believes the turtles of the Rushgore can be of use for provisioning and supplies.

'It occurs to me, [placeholder], that turtles of this size must lay enormous eggs. Such an egg might feed our entire party for a day or two.

'Would you perhaps seek out the turtles nesting-grounds and collect some of these eggs for me? Be careful not to drop any when you are carrying them back.

'I cannot wait to try such a delicacy....'
Turtle-eggs may be found at the turtle nesting-grounds to the south-east of the Woodman camp in the Rushgore.\n\nFrogildi has asked you to collect the turtles' eggs and bring them to her.
'Many thanks to you, [placeholder]! These shall do nicely.'
Turtle-eggs may be found at the turtle nesting-grounds to the south-east of the Woodman camp in the Rushgore.\n\nFrogildi has asked you to collect the turtles' eggs and bring them to her.
Frogildi is at the Woodman camp in the Rushgore, north-west of the turtle nesting-grounds.\n\nYou should speak with Frogildi regarding the eggs.
Bring the egg you collected to Frogildi at the Woodman-camp
Talk to Frogildi at the Woodman camp in the Rushgore
